text: Rudolf Krupitzer (April 18, 1879 - May 2, 1972) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1879 births Category:1972 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
